section.title: Locale codes
section.comment: Note: This list is synced with core/string/locales.h in the engine.
section.paragraph: Locale code has the following format: language_Script_COUNTRY_VARIANT, where:

list_item.paragraph: language - 2 or 3-letter language code, in lower case.
Script - optional, 4-letter script code, in title case.
COUNTRY - optional, 2-letter country code, in upper case.
VARIANT - optional, language variant, region and, sort order. A variant can have any number of underscored keywords.
